  "response": "San Sebastian (Donostia) offers several delicious and affordable dining options:\n\n1. Pintxos Bars\n- Bar Nestor (known for amazing pintxos)\n- La Cuchara de San Telmo\n- Bar Zeruko\n- Ganbara Jatetxea\n\n2. Casual Restaurants\n- Casa Gandarias\n- A Fuego Negro\n- Bodega Donostiarra\n- Taberna Erlo\n\n3. Budget-friendly Lunch Spots\n- Bar Martinez\n- La Mari\n- Bar Antonio\n- Astelena Jatetxea\n\nTips:\n- Pintxos bars are usually very affordable\n- Lunch menus (men\u00fa del d\u00eda) are typically cheaper than dinner\n- Old Town (Parte Vieja) has many budget-friendly options\n- Avoid tourist-heavy areas for better prices\n- Local markets like La Bretxa can also offer affordable, fresh food\n\nAverage pintxos price ranges from \u20ac1-3, making them an economical way to sample local cuisine.",
